{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are Bob, a big-headed sleepyhead, but this time when you wake up, everything has changed.  <br>Opening your foggy eyes, you find that your memories seem to have been stolen, leaving your mind completely blank. The room is pitch black; all the lights are off. Don't panic, Bob! With your head\u2014both comical and incredibly practical\u2014embark on a journey filled with puzzles, traps, and adventure!  <br><strong>Four batteries, four lights \u2013 the truth awaits you just ahead.</strong></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you ready? Shake off your daze, Bob, for destiny awaits you!</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Core Gameplay</strong></p></li></ul><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At the right moment, using your &quot;big head&quot; can trigger a perfect dodge, along with many additional effects.</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420590/extras/\u95ea\u907f\u5927\u6446\u9524.gif?t=1739160321\" /></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make full use of your dodge ability to pull off many incredible maneuvers.</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420590/extras/\u8fde\u7eed\u95ea\u907f.gif?t=1739160321\" /></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Main Objectives</strong></p></li></ul><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Adventure, combat, puzzles, and the collection of 4 batteries to uncover the truth behind your lost memories!</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/sto